# 1. Copy logo from Figma as SVG: https://www.figma.com/file/E1RJ5DNTM8eHZpJI1bcaP3/Public-logo?node-id=1-2&t=4PuwjeL9pH70lnxv-0
# 2. Crop & revert the colors (for dark), export to PNG.
